            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 48,
            "title": "About BrightTools",
            "content": "<p>BrightTools wants to make a world of difference in your life and inside your home. We want you to experience daily cleaning that’s fun, easy and as fresh as your floors. With every touch, with every sweep our cleaning tools are designed to feel different and to target dirt with minimum effort and maximum shine.</p><p>Born in Melbourne in 2018, we’re the exclusive suppliers of the Tyroler revolutionary range of high quality rubber, magnetic, 100% natural silicone and heavy-duty brooms, mops, dustpans, squeegees, window cleaners and more. </p>"
          }
        },
        "template--19386613530898__6102cdd6-471a-4da7-96c1-3d1c6ecd4fa8-168665268062273bb2-1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/About_us_1.png",
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 48,
            "title": "Solutions for Every Cleaning Problem",
            "content": "<p>With long-lasting benefits like ergonomic swivel heads and flexible handles for easy-reach in every corner of a room, rubber dust-pans that actually stick to the surface so dirt won’t fly and silicone brooms that work on versatile flooring from carpet to timber, you’ll find a solution for every cleaning problem with our smarter tool technology.</p>"
          }
        },
        "03265a34-0f5f-48b7-b94e-68fc30ab6827": {
