            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 48,
            "title": "Ethically-Made Premium Cleaning Tools",
            "content": "<p>No other brand is like us in Australia, we’ve got a handle on durability and sustainability, placing it right in the palm of your hands.</p><p>Our natural rubber bristles have an electrostatic charge that picks up the finest dirt and hair, giving you an ideal clean, and our floor wipes cover more surface and are fragrance fresh for everyday home maintenance that doesn’t feel like a chore. You’ll feel the difference with every product you clean with – and every product is so easy to clean.</p><p>A step up from the rest, our ethically-made premium cleaning tools will last you years, saving you time and promising customer satisfaction so Australian households feel bright at home.</p>"
